@startuml

title Diagrama de Secuencia: Validación del Wizard

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam roundcorner 5

actor "Usuario" as User
boundary "Navegador" as Browser
participant "FeatureNode\n(React)" as FN
participant "FeatureTreesContext" as Ctx
participant "StepComponent\n(useMemo)" as Step
participant "Django REST" as API
participant "FlamapyService\n(BDD)" as Flamapy

== 1. Evaluación reactiva (cada toggle) ==

User -> Browser : activa / desactiva feature
Browser -> FN : onChange event
FN -> Ctx : setTrees([{ features: [...] }])
Ctx --> Step : re-render
Step -> Step : useMemo recalcula\nintraViolations + incomingHints
note right of Step
  getViolations() — restricciones violadas por features seleccionadas
  getIncomingRequirements() — hints IMPLIES con antecedente activo
end note
Step --> Browser : render hints ámbar + estado del botón
Browser --> User : muestra hints / botón habilitado o bloqueado

== 2. Validación servidor (al pulsar "Listo") ==

User -> Browser : pulsa "Listo"
Browser -> Step : onClick
Step -> API : POST /api/v1/configurator/validate-features\n{ features, is_full, step }
activate API
API -> Flamapy : validate_features(features, is_full, step)
activate Flamapy
Flamapy -> Flamapy : pinear False features no seleccionadas\nBDD satisfiability check
alt configuración inválida
  Flamapy --> API : { valid: false, errors: [...] }
  deactivate Flamapy
  API --> Step : 400
  deactivate API
  Step --> Browser : render errores inline
  Browser --> User : muestra errores, paso bloqueado
else configuración válida
  Flamapy --> API : { valid: true }
  deactivate Flamapy
  API --> Step : 200 OK
  deactivate API
  Step --> Browser : render paso siguiente desbloqueado
  Browser --> User : muestra siguiente paso
end

@enduml
